      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯警告投资者不会相信未来的支出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 宣布进一步推迟支出限制，她将很难让金融城相信她的财政信誉，因为她已经试图将有政治争议的决定推迟到工党议会任期的结束阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普下令取消有利于电动汽车的政策和补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-end-to-electric-vehicle-mandate-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普下令其政府考虑取消有利于电动汽车的补贴和其他政策，此举奠定了可能减缓美国清洁汽车普及速度的举措基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-end-to-electric-vehicle-mandate-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划在 2 月 1 日前对墨西哥、加拿大征收 25% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，计划在 2 月 1 日前对墨西哥和加拿大征收高达 25% 的关税，重申他的观点，即美国的近邻和最大贸易伙伴正在让非法移民和毒品涌入美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多诺霍称欧洲需要立即就德拉吉报告采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/europe-needs-to-act-more-urgently-on-draghi-report-donohoe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区高级官员表示，欧盟需要加快努力提高竞争力，并实施前欧洲央行行长马里奥·德拉吉提出的一些建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/europe-needs-to-act-more-urgently-on-draghi-report-donohoe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
